       "Machine"."MachineName", isnull ("Action"."ASCName",
       N'N/A') as "Action", "FAMSession"."Queuing",
       "FAMSession"."Processing", case when "FAMSession"."StopTime" is
       null then N'Running' else N'Finished'
       end as "CurrentlyRunning", "FAMSession"."StopTime"
  from ((("dbo"."FAMSession" "FAMSession"
  inner join "dbo"."FPSFile" "FPSFile"
       on ("FPSFile"."ID" = "FAMSession"."FPSFileID"))
  inner join "dbo"."Machine" "Machine"
       on ("Machine"."ID" = "FAMSession"."MachineID"))
  left
  join "dbo"."Action" "Action"
       on ("Action"."ID" = "FAMSession"."ActionID"))
 where (("FPSFile"."FPSFileName" like N'ETL%')
       and (("FAMSession"."StartTime" >= DATEADD(MONTH,-1,GETDATE()) ) or not ((isnull
       (CharIndex (N':', "FPSFile"."FPSFileName"), 0) > 0))))
</Sql></Query><Query Type="SelectQuery" Name="AttributeSetForFile"><Tables><Table Name="AttributeSetForFile" X="100" Y="30" Width="125" Height="134" /></Tables><Columns><Column
